reviewText:
Impressive game. It brings together, with its light atmosphere, really challenging missions. The history is so cool and the way they combined action and strategy are bringing me a lot of fun! Still in the beginning, though (7 days, I think), but I can see the map I have to defend getting bigger, the enemies getting harder, and my traps inventory growing with new stuff. Really recommend!

Every night you will be attacked by wolves, werewolves, etc. So the game will be as follows:
-Cool history part (very brief and objetive);
-Preparation of traps to face the night;
-Face the enemies by yourself, because only the traps are never enough to all the enemies!
